{"tid":1568345,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（大家入黎）有樣嘢叫“非法拘捕”","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:59:40.000Z","uid":23179,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de1123b8f76ecc8fdc720b29a5a4a5d3d45ff4c9","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:21:56.000Z","msg":"有樣嘢叫&ldquo;非法拘捕&rdquo;，大家都要知。<br />\n<br />\n警察行使拘捕權嘅基礎有二：<br />\n<br />\n(1)法例有定明嘅罪犯，必須要符合法律內定明嘅控罪原素；<br />\n<br />\n(2)要有表面證據，姐係話表面上有理由相信某人犯咗法，呢點可以好濶，自稱自己見到或有人指稱某人犯法。如果冇調查就拉，可以嚴重到係非法拘捕或只係紀律處分。<br />\n<br />\n所以拉人嘅前題上述兩點缺一不可。差人話拉你就要佢回答上述問題，法律要求咩控罪原素。拉咗返差館要同值日官報警非法拘捕，第日告返拉人嗰個畜牲。非法拘捕係刑事罪行，可判監禁。<br />\n<br />\n由於畜牲拉人後要留書面紀錄，你又報案的話，佢就唔敢亂寫，砌你生豬肉都冇咁易。過後根據佢嘅書面紀錄反咬佢都易啲"},{"pid":"9403edcb423ab4c8231fe850582d2673d82427e5","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:22:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n代朋友開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37043eb6813c4fe650903b3c26c43679a7c7bbda","tid":1568345,"uid":23902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"咩時候啊 仲諗住同狗講道理？？？ 認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca4fc85fe37143e3bbccf05bd8f005d2f231e62","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"妨礙司法公正的行為包括：<br />\n為換取報酬而中止刑事檢控；提出虛假指控或證據；向調查人員提供虛假陳述；恐嚇或騷擾證人、陪審員或司法人員等。"},{"pid":"3231f64d752d768d5fe78870dd4b647e19e0dda1","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37043eb6813c4fe650903b3c26c43679a7c7bbda","tid":1568345,"uid":23902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"咩時候啊 仲諗住同狗講道理？？？ 認真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"之後告佢地就有用，保障自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a6850a374f4dfbe5e4d697ae10a77e49a62452","tid":1568345,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:26:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f211e9fe77cd284f9e5c8e9f559e53963da4f37","tid":1568345,"uid":310720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:26:46.000Z","msg":"班狗識閪聽人話咩"},{"pid":"39d11fe50c861500abf2902a22fd4ea4ca284976","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"普通法罪行:<br />\n在香港，妨礙司法公正是一項可公訴的普通法罪行。<br />\n簡單來說，妨礙司法公正是指阻撓、阻止、損害或阻礙法院或審裁處，在任何實際、即將、預期或可能進行的法庭程序中維持司法公正的能力。<br />\n<br />\n這項罪行是由一項 <br />\n<br />\n(1) 傾向並有意圖 <br />\n(2) 妨礙司法公正的 <br />\n(3) 行為或作為所構成。"},{"pid":"e1da204c418d79e61533393f2546792d27ec2add","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f460858e22e9afc38c7dd52e75eaff59774c5cd","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:29:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9dbe3bfc590d21d29c1a82f9d5514fc9cb37235","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749bb492a2fbcc6934a20df11e7503e58b75a7ac","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fedaac95866d5f1a8ed700d843bb6b87765aaac","tid":1568345,"uid":23179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:30:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630a793b33966c2f88ef4a66a1f23000c8468bab",